{"tid":840230,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每日都有衝動要掐死既人","createTime":"2018-09-28T14:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T15:04:41.000Z","uid":210709,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"55ed0e2d9d2da5521782b5293906a20e3be3ad76","tid":840230,"uid":210709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T14:24:12.000Z","msg":"求你放過我啦好嗎？放學搭巴士返屋企想休息下個腦，啲阿嬸阿叔好喜歡大大聲講電話，已經夠折磨人<br />\n<br />\n今日！我隔離個阿叔用緊方言大大聲講電話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  啲方言講到粗口咁，翻譯唔到，點解有咁多個「系」字，好難聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n理系伍系既小既系 系毛<br />\n系牙理mo貢貢系奶<br />\n牙培貢理day<br />\n理伍貢理系培下之系<br />\n努貢momo系之尼牙<br />\n挑鋼 系妹理下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你講完未<br />\n<br />\n嘿系小既系毛 毛系麻<br />\n理矛貢貢秘 貢家度毛系既<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阿叔終於落咗車，真係感謝主"},{"pid":"b42a1a58ec53a35a3619ef550234aeacd7234f02","tid":840230,"uid":1249,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T14:25:45.000Z","msg":"你做人都幾辛苦"},{"pid":"532769c23ce9a678d641de1611b37b391b0edb70","tid":840230,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T14:30:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64780cb9bf16d15a1ed837faf73ba13517ae081b","tid":840230,"uid":37431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T14:48:51.000Z","msg":"仲有咳唔遮口嘅廢物"},{"pid":"f74a28df6746983cb390d2fd5ad887606d928078","tid":840230,"uid":210709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"532769c23ce9a678d641de1611b37b391b0edb70","tid":840230,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T14:30:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"